title: Online share of retail trade in selected countries 2014 to 2018
summary: This grouped bar chart shows SOME LABEL on the Y-axis for 12 different Countrys for 5 groups 2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, and 2018 that are presented on the X-axis.
Country United Kingdom had the maximum SOME LABEL among all 5 groups, and it was for 2017. The minimum SOME LABEL was observed in Country Switzerland for 2014.
In Country United Kingdom, 2014 had the maximum SOME LABEL and it saw the lowest in Country Switzerland out of all 12 Countrys.
Country United Kingdom and Switzerland had the biggest gap of 134.0 between the highest and lowest SOME LABEL found for 2014.

max_summary: This grouped bar chart represents 12 different Countrys on X-axis for 5 groups 2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, and 2018. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding SOME LABEL.
Out of all 5 groups, 2017 had the highest SOME LABEL in Country United Kingdom and 2014 had the lowest SOME LABEL in Country Switzerland.
Among all the Countrys, 2014 had the highest SOME LABEL in Country United Kingdom and lowest SOME LABEL in Country Switzerland.
There is a gap of 134.0 between the highest and lowest SOME LABEL found for 2014 in Country United Kingdom and Switzerland.
Among the groups, 2017 had the biggest difference in SOME LABEL. Where the maximum SOME LABEL was 17.8 times larger than the minimum SOME LABEL.
2017 had the maximum SOME LABEL out of all 5 groups in Country United Kingdom followed by 2017 in United Kingdom, and the minimum SOME LABEL is found for 2014 in Switzerland.
On average, the Country United Kingdom had the highest SOME LABEL for all 5 groups 2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, and 2018. Whereas Italy had the lowest average SOME LABEL.
